{
  "chapter": 44,
  "chapter_summary": "小方与阳光伪装为夫妻加入花不拉的商队，途经藏边廉价小客栈投宿。花不拉是个矮小弯曲、手段残忍的商队头领，由大烟袋代言，他暗中试探小方并赠予匕首。小方与阳光被分派到普通商旅赵群夫妇隔壁，夜间赵胡氏房中传出的亲密声音令二人尴尬难眠。到了第三夜小方故意输掉骰子睡在车上，花不拉趁机潜入阳光房中意图不轨，言语威胁恐吓。阳光情急之下掷出包袱，包袱中一件物品落地，花不拉见状惊恐万分头也不回地逃走。那件神秘物品的出现，暗示阳光身上隐藏着不为人知的秘密。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你有没有练过武？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "text": "没有。虽然练过几天庄稼把式，也不能算练武。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你身上有没有带家伙？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "连一把刀都没有带？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你最好把这把家伙带在身上。你的老婆年纪还不算太大，我们这队伍里什么样的人都有，走在路上，能小心还是小心些好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那个人不是好人。绝对不是好人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我们来掷骰子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "掷骰子？你要跟我赌什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "谁输了今天晚上就睡到外面的车子上去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你来干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "来陪你。我知道你的老公不中用，特地来陪你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "text": "我不要你陪。你再不走我就要叫了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你叫？叫谁？叫你的老公？你就算把他叫来又有什么用？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你老公有没有我这样的功夫？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_la",
      "speaker_name": "花不拉",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你敢叫，我就塞住你的嘴，你的老公来了，我就把他活活捏死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    }
  ],
